# ChangeLog for net-ftp/proftpd
# Copyright 1999-2015 Gentoo Foundation; Distributed under the GPL v2
# $Header: /var/cvsroot/gentoo-x86/net-ftp/proftpd/ChangeLog,v 1.341 2015/07/03 08:56:27 ago Exp $

  03 Jul 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> proftpd-1.3.5a.ebuild:
  Stable for alpha, wrt bug #546644

  24 Jun 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> proftpd-1.3.5a.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc, wrt bug #546644

  11 Jun 2015; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> proftpd-1.3.5a.ebuild:
  arm stable, bug #546644

  03 Jun 2015; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> proftpd-1.3.5a.ebuild:
  Stable for PPC64 (bug #546644).

  01 Jun 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> proftpd-1.3.5a.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #546644

  01 Jun 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> proftpd-1.3.5a.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #546644

  01 Jun 2015; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> proftpd-1.3.5a.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #546644).

  30 May 2015; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org>
  -files/CVE-2015-3306-test.patch, -files/CVE-2015-3306.patch,
  -proftpd-1.3.5-r2.ebuild:
  Drop incorrectly backported patches: bug #550644 by Todd Goodman.

*proftpd-1.3.5a (30 May 2015)

  30 May 2015; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> +proftpd-1.3.5a.ebuild:
  Version bump: fixes security bug #546644 aka CVE-2015-3306: Unauthenticated
  copying of files via SITE CPFR/CPTO in mod_copy (USE=copy).

  30 May 2015; Ian Delaney <idella4@gentoo.org> proftpd-1.3.5-r2.ebuild:
  correction to the slot operator setting to dev-libs/openssl, noted by floppym

  29 May 2015; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> files/CVE-2015-3306.patch:
  Removed CVS expansion patch damage, but it does not fix USE=copy build failure
  yet.

*proftpd-1.3.5-r2 (27 May 2015)

  27 May 2015; Ian Delaney <idella4@gentoo.org> +files/CVE-2015-3306-test.patch,
  +files/CVE-2015-3306.patch, +proftpd-1.3.5-r2.ebuild:
  revbump; security patch (split into 2) wrt bug #546644, address qa issues by
  repoman for deps requiring slot operator

  11 Mar 2015; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> proftpd-1.3.5.ebuild:
  ppc64 stable wrt #518290

  15 Jan 2015; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> proftpd-1.3.5.ebuild:
  ia64/sparc stable wrt #518290

  28 Dec 2014; Aaron W. Swenson <titanofold@gentoo.org> proftpd-1.3.4d.ebuild,
  proftpd-1.3.4e.ebuild, proftpd-1.3.5.ebuild, proftpd-1.3.5-r1.ebuild:
  Rename virtual/postgresql to dev-db/postgresql

*proftpd-1.3.5-r1 (19 Dec 2014)

  19 Dec 2014; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> +proftpd-1.3.5-r1.ebuild:
  Enable 'dynmasq' and 'msg' modules for real (bug #533028 by Till Schäfer).

  20 Nov 2014; Tobias Klausmann <klausman@gentoo.org> proftpd-1.3.5.ebuild:
  Stable on alpha, bug 518290

  03 Nov 2014; Aaron W. Swenson <titanofold@gentoo.org> proftpd-1.3.4d.ebuild,
  proftpd-1.3.4e.ebuild, proftpd-1.3.5.ebuild:
  Update PostgreSQL dependencies and/or checks to virtual/postgresql.

  13 Aug 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> proftpd-1.3.5.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc, wrt bug #518290

  10 Aug 2014; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> proftpd-1.3.4d.ebuild,
  proftpd-1.3.4e.ebuild, proftpd-1.3.5.ebuild:
  QA: drop trailing '.' from DESCRIPTION

  10 Aug 2014; Andreas Schuerch <nativemad@gentoo.org> proftpd-1.3.5.ebuild:
  x86 stable, see bug 518290

  01 Aug 2014; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> proftpd-1.3.5.ebuild:
  arm stable, bug #518290

  31 Jul 2014; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> proftpd-1.3.5.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #518290).

  30 Jul 2014; Chema Alonso <nimiux@gentoo.org> proftpd-1.3.5.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64 wrt bug #518290

*proftpd-1.3.5 (16 May 2014)

  16 May 2014; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org>
  +files/proftpd-1.3.5-netaddr-segv.patch, +proftpd-1.3.5.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Version bump.

*proftpd-1.3.4e (16 May 2014)

  16 May 2014; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org>
  +files/proftpd-1.3.4e-link-tests.patch, +proftpd-1.3.4e.ebuild,
  -files/proftpd-1.3.4a-ubug-3682.patch, -files/proftpd-1.3.4a-ubug-3728.patch,
  -files/proftpd-1.3.4b-ubug-3795.patch,
  -files/proftpd-1.3.4c-fix-build-noipv6.patch, -proftpd-1.3.3g.ebuild,
  -proftpd-1.3.4a-r1.ebuild, -proftpd-1.3.4a.ebuild, -proftpd-1.3.4b.ebuild,
  -proftpd-1.3.4c-r1.ebuild, -proftpd-1.3.4c-r2.ebuild, -proftpd-1.3.4c.ebuild:
  Version bump (old stable branch).

