  +files/proftpd-1.3.4d-memset-fix.patch, proftpd-1.3.4d.ebuild:
  Fix memset argument (noticed by GCC).

*proftpd-1.3.4d (12 Sep 2013)

  12 Sep 2013; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org>
  +files/proftpd-1.3.4d-sftp-kbdint-max-responses-bug3973.patch,
  +proftpd-1.3.4d.ebuild:
  Version bump. Added fix for sftp kbdint security issue. Bug #484614 by
  Agostino Sarubbo.

*proftpd-1.3.4c-r2 (16 Jul 2013)

  16 Jul 2013; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> +proftpd-1.3.4c-r2.ebuild:
  Bump mod_vroot up to 0.9.3 from github repo (bug #476972 by Markus Lidel).

  14 Jul 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> proftpd-1.3.4c.ebuild:
  Stable for arm, wrt bug #476408

  07 May 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> proftpd-1.3.4c.ebuild:
  Stable for sparc, wrt bug #450746

