  23 Sep 2006; Luca Longinotti <chtekk@gentoo.org>
  +files/proftpd-1.3.0-mod_ctrls_sighup.patch, files/proftpd.rc6,
  proftpd-1.2.10-r7.ebuild, proftpd-1.3.0-r1.ebuild,
